Title : 2014 China International Challenger – Men's Singles
Text : {{TennisEvents|2014|China International Challenger|
| champ = {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Alex Bolt]]
| runner = {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Nikola Mektić]]
| score  = 6–2, 7–5
|before_name=ATP China International Tennis Challenge
}}

{{main|2014 China International Challenger}}
[[Márton Fucsovics]] was the defending champion. Australian [[Alex Bolt]] won his first Challenger title, with a 6–2, 7–5 defeat of Nikola Metkić in the final.

